  <main>
    <header class="text-center my-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 underline">Glaucoma Services at Birat Rani Aakha Aspatal</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-2">A New Standard in Eye Care and Compassionate Treatment</p>
    </header>

    <section class="container mx-auto p-4 space-y-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <img src="/public/img/galucoma.jpg" alt="Glaucoma Care" class="mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg cat-res">
      </div>
      <br>

      <article class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-blue-500">Comprehensive Glaucoma Services</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
          <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Birat Rani Aakha Aspatal</span> is setting a new standard in glaucoma care, combining advanced technology with compassionate service to combat this sight-threatening disease.
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-8 space-y-2">
          <li>
            <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">State-of-the-art diagnostics:</span> Utilizing advanced tools like tonometry and Humphrey Field Analyzer for precise detection and monitoring of glaucoma.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Innovative treatments:</span> Offering cutting-edge procedures such as Nd YAG Laser iridotomy and transscleral cyclophotocoagulation, ensuring effective, tailored management for each patient.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Expert care team:</span> Led by experienced ophthalmologists who provide personalized treatment plans and ongoing support to each patient, ensuring optimal care and comfort.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-blue-500">Accessible and Affordable</h2>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-8 space-y-2">
          <li>
            <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Transparent pricing:</span> Competitive rates ensure that high-quality glaucoma care is affordable and accessible to all, without compromising on service or results.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Community outreach:</span> Through regular screening camps and educational programs, Birat Rani Aakha Aspatal is dedicated to raising awareness and promoting early detection in underserved communities.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-blue-500">Preserving Vision, Enhancing Lives</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
          At <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Birat Rani Aakha Aspatal</span>, patients receive not only cutting-edge glaucoma treatment but also a commitment to preserving vision and enhancing quality of life. Our mission is to ensure that every patient enjoys the benefits of advanced technology and compassionate care. <span class="font-bold text-blue-600">Experience the future of eye care today!</span>
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>
